('37bd371c-df34-4268-9335-019b9c850576', NULL, 'adfb2457-819c-4574-ace1-56f5b38d8f96', NULL, '', '', '', '', 'dresden', 'Tanzsportclub Casino Dresden e.V.', 'Der Tanzsportclub Casino Dresden e.V. bietet für alle Altersgruppen\r\nMöglichkeiten der aktiven Freizeitgestaltung in familiärer Atmosphäre.\r\n\r\nNeben den traditionellen Disziplinen der Standard- und Lateintänze\r\nim Turniertanzsport und Breitensport, gehört auch Salsa, Discofox und\r\nIrish Dance zu unserem Angebot.\r\n\r\nDie Bereiche Kindertanz und Jugendarbeit liegen uns besonders am Herzen.\r\nSchon jetzt sind in unserem Verein die "Kleinsten" ab einem Alter von\r\n5 Jahren mit Spaß und Freude am Tanzsport dabei. Auch in Zukunft werden\r\nwir den Kinder- und Jugendbereich stärken und fördern. Konkrete Projekte\r\nwerden bereits realisiert oder sind in Planung.', '', 'http://www.tsc-casino.de', '', '0171 / 75 69 536', 'sports', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', 1, NULL, 0, '587d03088ce68', 'de', '2017-01-16 18:29:44', '2017-01-16 18:29:44'),
('37e0e3ef-6e5c-4902-99a7-71df410154f2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'House "Schieferburg" for children and youths', 'The youth club "Schieferburg" in Gruna is a project of open youth work and an institution of the Stadtjugendring Dresden e.V. It is our goal to offer children and young people a space, where they can meet on a self-determined basis, receive help, where they can participate in the events and take part in the decision-making. The range of offers, which are targeted at all age groups, include:\r\n\r\n*Open offers in the café (join-in activities, games, service package, XBOX, video)\r\n\r\n*Table tennis, billiard, table soccer, dart, air hockey, trampoline\r\n\r\n*Creative activities (crafting, pottery, sewing)\r\n\r\n*Soccer, streetball, volleyball\r\n\r\n*Workshops (circus, sewing)\r\n\r\n*Projects (radio station, percussion, kitchen for children, dance projects, sewing projects, pottery projects)\r\n\r\n*Excursions, trips, youth travel ( e.g. sledding, paddling, hiking)\r\n\r\n*Computer workshop and multimedia offerings\r\n\r\n*Off-site events with open character (e.g. district festivals, fountain festivals)\r\n\r\n*On-site events of competitive character (sports, cooking, talent show)\r\n\r\n*Help and counselling', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '56165f2b94c88', 'en', '2016-08-26 10:58:11', '2016-08-26 10:58:11'),
